    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 捕捉。编辑。修饰。</h2>结合 AI 智能的照片编辑软件<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故障特效来做到画面分裂</h2>拆分和组合颜色层，并围绕一个主题展现无限变化。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/678fe7ee51b18c705365bb2ee0193c2d.avif?t=1754573563\" width=444 height=264 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI 天空置换</h2>AI 置换天空工具，让你可以为照片换上一个全新的天空，还能设置动态效果、更改样式、混合特效与重新定位，瞬间转换相片天空背景，带来不同氛围。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/2天空置换.png?t=1754573563\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 展现您的真实色彩</h2>细部调整画面色调、饱和度、阴影等，精准掌控色彩与光线，彻底体现您的设计风格。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/3_true_color.PNG?t=1754573563\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >点亮你的照片</h2>使用散景创建梦幻般的图像，添加自然光彩、闪光和强烈的光晕。编辑从大小、颜色和方向的所有内容，以极其丰富的光线真正塑造您的场景。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/08607832107d716822708bbb2536ec14.avif?t=1754573563\" width=420 height=262 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 强大 AI 工具，一键打造传神之作</h2>透过 AI 技术，一键快速自然地移除照片中不想要的人物或对象，还您干净美照！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/5_AI对象移除.jpg?t=1754573563\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 精准的图层编辑</h2>透过强大且直观的图层编辑工具，细部调整图片细节，打造精美作品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/fa0f761bd17db5054a3af49e276f083c.avif?t=1754573563\" width=600 height=348 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 完美修饰照片</h2>从快速的照片编修到精细地大幅改造，大量专业又易操作的修图工具，使每一张照片看起来都完美无瑕。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/7修饰照片.PNG?t=1754573563\" /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > RAW 档编辑</h2>由于相片大师支持所有专业文件格式和最流行的相机，因此可以打破您的创作限制。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115640/extras/8_RAW.PNG?t=1754573563\" /></span></h2></ul>",
